    "name": "Sotetsu Fresa Inn Nagoyaeki Sakuradoriguchi",
    "detail": "As a hotelier in Singapore, I find this hotel is really good, when first entered the hotel the staff will greet you. The amenities that hotel provides is more than what a 3 star hotel will do. Tea bags with more than 8 flavors, facial mask, bathing salt, cleansing oil, foam etc are provided at lobby for all guest to take. There's even vending machines, coin self washing machine ice maker and microwave oven for guest to used. Even when my room is under DO NOT DISTURB (not to clean the room) when I'm back at night , HK team actually placed 2 bags outside my room with fresh towels and etc. Nothing I can ask for more. Just highly recommended and will surely stay here again.",
